ygData.msgSnippet: At you groups level it is very possible to for your party to solo Death beetles and tormented dead.  If you stay on the right side of the house (the gazebo)
ygData.messageBody:
At you groups level it is very possible to for your party to solo Death
beetles and tormented dead. If you stay on the right side of the house
(the gazebo) you should be able to pull them one by one with your lull
song. It was great xp and will shot you from 14 to 16 very quickly. The
only problem stems from the fact that it is very easy to be trained by
beetles and undead and on my server it is grand central station at times.

Treilanin Loreweaver
Honour Guard, Karana
